==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*μυστήριον / mustērion / moos-tay'-ree-on
*From a derivative of μύω muō (to shut the mouth); a secret or “mystery” (through the idea of silence imposed by initiation into religious rites): 

===Noun===
'''μυστήριον'''

# [[mystery]].

